 TSHWANE - Councillor Murunwa Makwarela has been reinstated as Tshwane Mayor after he provided a letter of solvency to the municipality's City Manager. Makwarela was previously disqualified by the Independent Electoral Commission. READ: City of Tshwane mayorless again The IEC previously flagged him as an unrehabilitated insolvent. Watch the video above for more details on this story.